{"tid":383291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「得之，我幸；失之，我命」","createTime":"2017-09-01T10:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T12:05:31.000Z","uid":52013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a81899e332050c518b5e166c116f911168bfe084","tid":383291,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:58:49.000Z","msg":"冥冥中自有主宰。<br />\n命裡有時終須有，命裡無時莫強求。<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打覺得好多野都係整定<br />\n非人力可左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71f5bc17ee789be4028892ca5674e729d40ca67","tid":383291,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:02:49.000Z","msg":"盡人事 安天命"},{"pid":"25c13148ef414fd2b2990ac7f77d51431483b76a","tid":383291,"uid":117985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:08:20.000Z","msg":"雖然人定勝天係有可能發生。<br />\n但其實係呢個世界上有好多野我哋都係控制唔到，所以我都好相信有啲嘢其實係整定。<br />\n所以我都會覺得人世間成敗得失，係編排左。<br />\n個天唔會俾你一直衰落去，亦都唔會俾你永遠好落去。<br />\n好多野都無需刻意追求，隨遇而安先啱。<br />\n做人又何必執着呢"},{"pid":"915cbac53d5762291ad83d3498d4d43b03a266da","tid":383291,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>盡人事 安天命</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唯有係咁"},{"pid":"a68774fd5978a288e92eec4a2f99af237e5cf107","tid":383291,"uid":107656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"一切皆是命<br />\n半點不由人"},{"pid":"41fcfdff88761e5cabf519169fbd37e17a8e45fb","tid":383291,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:01:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然人定勝天係有可能發生。<br />\n但其實係呢個世界上有好多野我哋都係控制唔到，所以我都好相信有啲嘢其實係整定。<br />\n所以我都會覺得人世間成敗得失，係編排左。<br />\n個天唔會俾你一直衰落去，亦都唔會俾你永遠好落去。<br />\n好多野都無需刻意追求，隨遇而安先啱。<br />\n做人又何必執着呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地只係樂曲上既音符<br />\n而非編曲師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉"},{"pid":"656e47b700a0f5317c48fbfbfb2db9990a708578","tid":383291,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:01:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一切皆是命<br />\n半點不由人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我命由天不由我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec60f00b7e4cdea938e202988b139a11ba85cf72","tid":383291,"uid":2313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0aba487837af3ca6063a74d7f60fb686a7633fa","tid":383291,"uid":36791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:02:16.000Z","msg":"感情又點計？"},{"pid":"8848cf79ddba0e50541547c0577d578aa9f85db5","tid":383291,"uid":1348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:03:15.000Z","msg":"要怪就怪你老豆射精前無諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd206916fa34433f4116ad7408ad4d4ca51f7a0c","tid":383291,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:04:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>感情又點計？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n情愛既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望你唔會好似我個名咁"},{"pid":"06026ef331025d156c96f6b4a33abf3278bf7bd9","tid":383291,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:05:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要怪就怪你老豆射精前無諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 整定既 整定既"}]}